                <mxCell id="6-mfiE0Ln5hXqk0lmSrI-273" value="&lt;p class=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-weight:bold;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Insufficient Documentation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;0&quot;&gt;  &amp;nbsp;  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;22. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;&quot;&gt;배포 시점에서 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Original Society&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;&quot;&gt;가 자체 데이터베이스와 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;CIS-Net&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;&quot;&gt;을 상담한 후&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;&quot;&gt;부족한 문서 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;&quot;&gt;문서가 없거나 부분적인 문서&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;&quot;&gt;로 작업이 사용되는 경우&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;&quot;&gt;다음과 같이 분배해야 합니다&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;0&quot;&gt;  &amp;nbsp;  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;a. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;&quot;&gt;원본 권리자 중 하나가 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Receiving Society&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;&quot;&gt;에 속하는 회원이나 저작권 소유자로 식별될 경우 작품에 발생하는 모든 로열티를 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Receiving Society&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;&quot;&gt;에 분배합니다&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;&quot;&gt;또는&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;b. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;&quot;&gt;대안으로 원본 권리자 및 그들의 해당하는 점유율이 하나 이상의 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Sister Society&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;&quot;&gt;에 속하는 것으로 식별될 경우&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;&quot;&gt;해당 작품에 대한 발생 로열티는 각 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Sister Society&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;&quot;&gt;에 해당하는 점유율에 따라 분배될 수 있습니다&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div data-jsonlen=&quot;8778&quot; data-hjsonver=&quot;1.0&quot; class=&quot;hwp_editor_board_content&quot; id=&quot;hwpEditorBoardContent&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;mso-pagination:none;text-autospace:none;mso-padding-alt:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;&quot; class=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Receiving Society&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;&quot;&gt;도 부족한 문서 로열티를 수령할 때 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Binding Resolutions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:함초롬바탕;mso-fareast-font-family:함초롬바탕;&quot;&gt;와 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-farea