2pt; letter-spacing: 0pt;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 15px; background-color: initial; font-family: iRtcApFHHvWcWGLyUuV_; text-indent: -33.2pt;&quot;&gt;해당년도의 지상파방송 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 15px; background-color: initial; font-family: iRtcApFHHvWcWGLyUuV_; text-indent: -33.2pt; letter-spacing: 0pt;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 15px; background-color: initial; font-family: iRtcApFHHvWcWGLyUuV_; text-indent: -33.2pt;&quot;&gt;사&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 15px; background-color: initial; font-family: iRtcApFHHvWcWGLyUuV_; text-indent: -33.2pt; letter-spacing: 0pt;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;(KBS, MBC, SBS)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 15px; background-color: initial; font-family: iRtcApFHHvWcWGLyUuV_; text-indent: -33.2pt;&quot;&gt;의 라디오&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 15px; background-color: initial; font-family: iRtcApFHHvWcWGLyUuV_; text-indent: -33.2pt; letter-spacing: 0pt;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;, TV &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 15px; background-color: initial; font-family: iRtcApFHHvWcWGLyUuV_; text-indent: -33.2pt;&quot;&gt;분배자료로 분배&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 15px; font-family: iRtcApFHHvWcWGLyUuV_; background-color: initial; text-indent: -33.2pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 15px; font-family: iRtcApFHHvWcWGLyUuV_; background-color: initial; text-indent: -33.2pt;&quot;&gt;웹ㅋ캐스팅 : 매장음악서비스 :&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 15px; font-family: iRtcApFHHvWcWGLyUuV_; background-color: initial; text-indent: -32.7pt;&quot;&gt;저작권 사용료 납부 상위 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 15px; font-family: iRtcApFHHvWcWGLyUuV_; background-color: initial; text-indent: -32.7pt; letter-spacing: 0pt;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 15px; font-family: iRtcApFHHvWcWGLyUuV_; background-color: initial; text-indent: -32.7pt;&quot;&gt;개&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; text-indent: -32.7pt; font-size: 15px; font-family: iRtcApFHHvWcWGLyUuV_;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; text-indent: -32.7pt; font-size: 15px; font-family: iRtcApFHHvWcWGLyUuV_;&quot;&gt;웹캐스팅 개인방송 등 :&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; font-size: 15px; font-family: iRtcApFHHvWcWGLyUuV_; text-indent: -34.8pt;&quot;&gt;방송&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; font-size: 15px; font-family: iRtcApFHHvWcWGLyUuV_; text-indent: -34.8pt; letter-spacing: 0pt;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; font-size: 15px; font-family: iRtcApFHHvWcWGLyUuV_; text-indent: -34.8pt;&quot;&gt;전송&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; font-size: 15px; font-family: iRtcApFHHvWcWGLyUuV_; text-indent: -34.8pt; letter-spacing: 0pt;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; font-size: 15px; font-family: iRtcApFHHvWcWGLyUuV_; text-indent: -34.8pt;&quot;&gt;공연&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; font-size: 15px; font-family: iRtcApFHHvWcWGLyUuV_; text-indent: -34.8pt; letter-spacing: 0pt;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; font-size: 15px; font-family: iRtcApFHHvWcWGLyUuV_; text-indent: -34.8pt;&quot;&gt;복제 매체 비율을 토대로 징수금액을 구분하고&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; font-size: 15px; font-family: iRtcApFHHvWcWGLyUuV_; text-indent: -34.8pt; letter-spacing: 0pt;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;, &lt;/span&gt;